Description.value:
This iFlow replicates customers from SAP ERP to YaaS using the DEBMAS iDoc. 
If the YaaS customer is not existing, it will be created. If the YaaS customer exists, the data will be updated. The update will be done only if the attributes are different and an update is needed.
Besides of the main customer attributes also the entire iDoc is stored in the iDoc_DEBMAS mixin. In this way also ERP specific fields are stored on the YaaS customer object. 
If the ERP customer is marked for archiving, this information will be also stored in the mixin. Deletion of the YaaS customers is not presupposed.
